is very hard.

891
01:27:35,359 --> 01:27:38,600
You have to take good care of
and support this child well.

892
01:27:39,359 --> 01:27:41,600
Make its life in this world worth living.

893
01:27:53,199 --> 01:27:54,439
Are you leaving already?

894
01:27:55,000 --> 01:27:57,359
I have urgent business.
I have to fly home.

895
01:27:57,439 --> 01:27:58,640
Can I help you in any way?

896
01:27:59,640 --> 01:28:01,119
No. But thanks.

897
01:28:01,920 --> 01:28:03,159
Do visit us again.

898
01:28:05,960 --> 01:28:08,960
By then, you will have had your baby.

899
01:28:13,520 --> 01:28:15,479
Make sure you take good care of it.

900
01:29:10,039 --> 01:29:11,720
We just drive across the border.

901
01:29:11,800 --> 01:29:15,560
Once we've delivered the stuff,
we'll get all the money, bro.

902
01:29:15,640 --> 01:29:16,479
Take a look.

903
01:29:16,560 --> 01:29:17,600
He threatened

904
01:29:17,680 --> 01:29:18,720
to make this public.

905
01:29:18,800 --> 01:29:20,039
Your father had a fall.

906
01:29:20,119 --> 01:29:22,760
Won't you go and visit him?

907
01:29:22,840 --> 01:29:24,199
Stop! Freeze!

908
01:29:24,279 --> 01:29:25,680
Put the weapon down!

909
01:29:27,680 --> 01:29:28,520
Turn, bro!

910
01:29:33,359 --> 01:29:35,039
Officers! My son is there!

911
01:29:38,279 --> 01:29:39,800
We've surrounded the suspects.

912
01:29:39,880 --> 01:29:41,000
They won't get away.

913
01:29:41,079 --> 01:29:42,119
We're doomed!

914
01:29:43,399 --> 01:29:44,560
Give yourselves up!

915
